USING Progress.Lang.*.

BLOCK-LEVEL ON ERROR UNDO, THROW.

CLASS Card: 
  
  DEFINE PROPERTY cType AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO 
    GET. 
    SET.
    
  DEFINE PROPERTY iValue AS INTEGER NO-UNDO
    GET.
    SET.

  CONSTRUCTOR PUBLIC Card():
    SUPER ().    
  END CONSTRUCTOR.
  
  METHOD PUBLIC LOGICAL compareCardType(INPUT ipoCard AS CLASS Card):
    RETURN THIS-OBJECT:cType = ipoCard:cType.
  END METHOD.

  DESTRUCTOR PUBLIC Card():
  END DESTRUCTOR.

END CLASS.